WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:01.400
He loves me.

00:01.918 --> 00:02.937
<i>Senator Harding?</i>

00:03.073 --> 00:07.074
But America needs him
and so I have to sacrifice.

00:07.109 --> 00:09.609
In three weeks Paddy Ryan
is taking over

00:09.643 --> 00:11.143
as chief clerk
of the fourth ward.

00:11.177 --> 00:13.111
Jimmy here'll be
Pat's man Friday.

00:13.145 --> 00:16.012
- What's your name, handsome?
- Nelson.

00:17.981 --> 00:19.515
You were 13 years old.

00:19.549 --> 00:21.883
I was one of
King Neptune's consorts.

00:21.917 --> 00:25.317
Your father saw me and
Nucky brought me to him.

00:25.352 --> 00:27.118
I'm dying, boy.
Where are you going?

00:27.152 --> 00:29.286
I'm not quite sure what
you're getting at, sweetie.

00:29.320 --> 00:31.621
This morning I found
this in his house

00:31.655 --> 00:34.324
hidden in the kitchen.

00:34.358 --> 00:37.126
- Half the team is indicted.
- What do you propose?

00:37.160 --> 00:40.230
Come here to Chicago.
I want you to think hard

00:40.264 --> 00:43.032
about who in this town
is willing to do you a favor.

00:44.401 --> 00:46.602
There are four more
brothers plus Luciano.

00:46.637 --> 00:48.337
How are we supposed
to get to them now?

00:48.372 --> 00:50.006
Pack lightly.
We'll meet here.

00:50.040 --> 00:51.574
Where are the Dittrichs?

00:51.609 --> 00:54.177
Snuck out yesterday,
dead of night.

00:55.613 --> 00:57.747
- Fletcher gets elected.
- You're telling me?

00:57.781 --> 00:59.448
This is my life on the line!

00:59.483 --> 01:01.884
- I'm making a change.
- Eli's out?

01:01.918 --> 01:05.354
Deputy Halloran, the star is yours
to wear, if you'll honor us so.

01:05.388 --> 01:06.722
Sure I will.

01:06.756 --> 01:08.056
I need men I can trust.

01:08.091 --> 01:09.791
You can trust me, God damn it.

01:09.826 --> 01:11.326
<i>What do I have to do
to convince you?</i>

01:11.361 --> 01:14.296
Look, what do you expect me...

01:18.235 --> 01:20.070
I won't have another child.

01:20.104 --> 01:21.605
That's not
your right to decide.

01:21.639 --> 01:24.407
What purpose did it serve
to make me a widow?

01:24.442 --> 01:27.377
I have not lost one second
of sleep over what was done.

01:27.412 --> 01:29.379
Neither have you.

01:31.615 --> 01:34.850
<i>- When I came back...
- They had disappeared.</i>

